==English==

===Etymology===
From the {{etyl|ang|en}} [[pronominal adverb]] {{term|therfore|lang=ang}}; see {{term|there|lang=en}}, {{term|fore|lang=en}}, and {{term|for|lang=en}}. Compare {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|daarvoor|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|da|-}} and {{etyl|no|-}} {{term|derfor|lang=da}}, {{etyl|sv|-}} {{term|därför|lang=sv}}, {{term|därföre|lang=lv}}.

